{"tid":1768713,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《流水社運的原則》 - 陳雲","createTime":"2019-12-04T09:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T09:53:19.000Z","uid":69753,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3168e023142ed0631dc90d9f1279a408960d4c27","tid":1768713,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:14:32.000Z","msg":"《流水社運的原則》 - 陳雲<br />\n一、無名無姓。沒行動組織，蒙面，不接受採訪，不公開談論，隨說隨掃，不留下秘密談論的記錄或痕跡。<br />\n二、不言不語。不發言，不公開訴求，不寫大字報。<br />\n三、聚散無踪。不長期佔領，隨時解散，隨時聚合，行動的後續不定。直至香港普選為止。<br />\n<br />\n另外，差役會攻擊記者，因此差役可透過此方法扣查未經後期的影片。同時，香港媒體作訪問時，甚少會比受訪者簽署個人私隱文件，例如攝錄的訪問會到邊度同有咩相關人士會處理影片。因此他們可以話冇任何責任保護義士。"},{"pid":"6b8c3475a1842cee9f11078f592863e0870fb519","tid":1768713,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:15:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e8e85a563852cfd596d687a76b25bed555bc72a","tid":1768713,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"又係熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81dc098948acbd75ee5003bdf379756675a3906","tid":1768713,"uid":69753,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0e8e85a563852cfd596d687a76b25bed555bc72a","tid":1768713,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"又係熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"可否對事不對人？"},{"pid":"6d7d78ec0c116c0600e89c9affc6c4fba01b2d4b","tid":1768713,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e8e85a563852cfd596d687a76b25bed555bc72a","tid":1768713,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"又係熱狗<img 